---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import FAQSection from '@/components/sections/FAQSection.astro';

const faqItems = [
  {
    question: 'What does "100 free pages" mean?',
    answer: 'All document extractions via our web portal or through APIs are counted as 1 API call.<br/><br/>On free plan, your first 100 calls are on us for you to try out FormX.ai and feel free to contact us if you need help.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Do you save or encrypt any uploaded document?',
    answer: 'We only save the master document uploaded to our web portal, or the documents you uploaded for training a custom models. Any images uploaded via API or web portal test are in-memory only and disposed once extraction is done. We will not use your document for optimizing our AI models or any other purposes unless you request us to do so.<br/><br/>All API calls are encrypted with HTTPS.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Do you offer volume discount or private cloud deployment?',
    answer: 'Yes, we work with enterprises to customize the plan that suits their needs. Please contact us!<br/>',
  },
  {
    question: 'May I have a different SLA on latency and throughput of the API calls?',
    answer: 'Yes! We provide tailor-made SLA commitment for Enterprise Clients, please contact us!<br/>\u200d<br/>For Business Plan, the minimal throughput is 180 RPM (Requests per Min) for API call without Product Line Item, or 30 RPM for API call with Product Line Item, without a SLA commitment.',
  },
  {
    question: 'Where do you host FormX.ai and process the data?',
    answer: 'FormX.ai is hosted on GCP and Azure cloud; You can choose between United State, Taiwan and Singapore when create new project if you want to specify the region of data processing.<br/>',
  },
  {
    question: 'What is the accuracy for receipt extractions?',
    answer: 'Accuracy rate depends on a lot of factors, and it also depends on how accuracy are defined.<br/><br/>As a reference, most of our previous clients would have at least 70% of accuracy by fields.<br/><br/>If we limit to only images with good quality (no blur, no lighting problems), from our client\'s feedback, general fields such as date, time &amp; amount can have accuracies over 90%.<br/><br/>You can contact us with around 100 receipts as sample, and we will share an accuracy report with you.',
  },
  {
    question: 'What are the latency for receipt processing?',
    answer: 'Usually it is 4 - 8 seconds, excluding the image uploading time. (It is not a SLA commitment)<br/><br/>Image uploading time will depend on the image file size and network speed, which we have no control on. We suggest you to resize the images to a smaller one to reduce the uploading time.<br/><br/>If you need a better latency or a SLA commitment, please contact us for an Enterprise plan.',
  },
];
---

<PageLayout
