      <h1 data-w-id="727a87c6-748b-6e23-bcc5-fea53b0f3df8" class="title pricing">FormX.ai Pricing:<br/>&#x200D;<span class="text-highlight">Streamline Your Data, Scale Your Success</span></h1>
      <p data-w-id="727a87c6-748b-6e23-bcc5-fea53b0f3dfa">Transform tedious paperwork into instant insights with FormX.ai, your AI-powered solution for effortless data extraction and streamlined workflows.</p>
